      "text": "A family in FSM was missing for a week. Our Joint Rescue Sub-Center Guam team was notified and coordinated the search. USCGC Midgett, already on patrol for our U.S. Navy partners, diverted and found them in 10-foot seas after midnight on Monday. \n\nAll three are home safe. That's the mission. That's presence and partnerships in action!  \n\nRead more: https://t.co/ExXirgrCtW",
